==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Biquadrate
<hw>Bi*quad"rate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>bi-</ets> + <ets>quadrate</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>The
fourth power, or the square of the square. Thus 4x4=16, the square of 4,
and 16x16=256, the <xex>biquadrate</xex> of 4.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Biquadratic</ent>⟦br⟧
